{"tid":1551232,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港獨立與加入美國聯邦聯署已經開始","createTime":"2019-09-08T02:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T08:25:37.000Z","uid":292710,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fc174b61ba4924607d914eb05b92032eabf0410f","tid":1551232,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"快ｄ推到十萬人，共享成為美國公民既權利啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-independence-and-join-north-america-state\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-independence-and-join-north-america-state&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=645c7a9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-independence-and-join-north-america-state</a>"},{"pid":"461c5fa2eba16d2317c761670da3bf520ebff0c0","tid":1551232,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"即刻簽!"},{"pid":"601f9a23dc7f49c36c70e8f1ba1dffa3f6d45d23","tid":1551232,"uid":20723,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEqbc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEqbc4.png&h=1f16fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=732d56c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢"},{"pid":"cd20506002a1aade22a698bb2883bcc544828277","tid":1551232,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"人地想要先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申而家去簽"},{"pid":"a9060408764efea98d01c11a222140ded4122f34","tid":1551232,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"我要入合眾國啊hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aaf763299709956cb0f79917e4bcc234b31d5d4","tid":1551232,"uid":74929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"908 美領 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db92892c836c32083bc114ed5977add619952808","tid":1551232,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d0da71a77fa2ed1d7cbde007ff48d0122d4332","tid":1551232,"uid":5303,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:08:41.000Z","msg":"越黎越膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5eeacc00a9b3eb573fe4558d88b3c92fa86152a","tid":1551232,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"41d0da71a77fa2ed1d7cbde007ff48d0122d4332","tid":1551232,"uid":5303,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:08:41.000Z","msg":"越黎越膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"夠十萬就好笑"},{"pid":"6884897de01fce1eadcbfcd73ca3cc6f9fe7f4a3","tid":1551232,"uid":40543,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"負皮 上頁 勿推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bce29389028996ff532d00154085f899289aa4b","tid":1551232,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,